transcript:
Customer: Hello
Customer: Sir, ye bhi sold out ho gaya. 
Executive: Ha ji sir.
Customer: Call kiya to mujhe dikha kar diya. Website development ki lead bhi dikh rahi hai, kuch bhi nahi hai sab gayab hai ye hamare se. Pure do teen week ho gaye. Abhi tak kuch bhi website development ki ek bhi lead nahi paayi.
Executive: Sir, humne to kuch bhi nahi kiya. Aapne kuch ek block mein change kiya tha kya?
Customer: Nahi kiya sir, maine kuch bhi change. Mujhe time hi nahi mila. Mujhe laga shayad aap changes ke liye call kar rahe hain. Mere ko time nahi mila changes karne. Aapne call kiya.
Customer: Aap hai na mere ye lead nahi dikh rahi. Aap lead dekho na website development ki jitni bhi kya teen do teen week. 
Executive: Sir jab lead aayengi, sir lead aayengi to aapko dikhengi.
Customer: To hai hi nahi aapke paas lead hi nahi hai.
Executive: Sir, sir basically lead agar client post karega, requirement agar hogi to wo aapko dikhengi. Main yehi keh rahi hu.
Customer: Are main ye bol raha hu ki madam waha website development ki lead dikh rahi hai, faltu lead dikh rahi hai. Wo lead nahi chahiye na, uska kya matlab.
Customer: Hmm, ho gaya na.
Executive: Thik hai sir, main ji ji main aapko.
Customer: Ye to phone mat lagana.
Executive: Thik hai Sunil sir. Aapne open kara. Website development mein aapko lead hi nahi dikhi aap ye keh rahe hain, hai na?
Customer: Are kuch bhi lead bolti likhte ho be. Ye to aap hi log ne bola hai na ki aap dekhna dekhna ye chalu karna to main wapis chalu kiya na dekhna to kuch bhi nahi hai.
Executive: Thik hai sir aapko. Thik hai sir thik hai na phone mat lagana mujhe gali padegi nahi to.
Executive: Sir main check kar leti hu. Fir wo aapka personal view hai sir. Main ek bar check kar leti hu main aapko information de dungi.
Customer: Aap phone mat laga dena mere ko dobara.
summary:
Concerns:

- Website development leads not visible.

- Dissatisfied with the quality of leads.



Resolution:

- Executive assured to check the issue.



Next Steps: 

- Executive will check and provide information.



Alert (If Any):

None

@@@Sentiment:

- Angry -> Satisfied



@@@Key Topics:

- buyleads, website development, lead visibility
